701256f-a.title: Bronx: Hicks Street - Eastchester Road
701256f-a.text:
Hicks Street (running from right to left, on which school and low
buildings are facing), north side, west from Eastchester Road (right)
to Wilson Ave., showing Public School No. 78 at the N.E. corner of
Tish Ave. The vantage point is the north side of Boston Road at Corsa
Ave.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
